  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0baa\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Speaker will officially announce President Kota's resignation today",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Speaker Mahinda Yappa Abeywardena will officially announce the resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa this morning.",
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has sent a letter of resignation to the Speaker yesterday (14) following the intensification of the people's protest.",
        "The letter regarding the Speaker has been sent to the Legislature for legal advice and it is expected that the Speaker will officially announce the resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa to the people today.",
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa, who left the country for the Maldives after protesters besieged the Presidential Palace, announced his resignation through the Speaker after arriving in Singapore on Thursday (14) evening.",
        "Gotabaya Rajapaksa is considered to be the first president since Sri Lanka's independence to resign before the end of his term."
      ],
